{"tid":1464730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"請推！大家停止再嘈，文宣時候到","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:27:10.000Z","uid":244653,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d8017f644e03e0e5f6c3adeec0a18be7b982d327","tid":1464730,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"機場件事做左就做左<br />\n<br />\n大家要學一個中國詞彙叫「定性」<br />\n<br />\n咩叫定性？就係今晚在各大網絡做文宣，先定義個公安係搞事<br />\n<br />\n「中國公安混入和平示威中！」<br />\n「機場內地客內藏木棍，竟是...亅<br />\n「公安鬧事，人民聲討」<br />\n「警方例牌遅到，難道....亅<br />\n<br />\n唔需要有真正內容，就算淨標題就ok，總之帶起陰謀論，要學會五毛藍絲手段，先行定性，為行動正當化，各位手足，為今日冇出而自責？出手時候到了，各位盡做啊"},{"pid":"13399980dfe13c334011ddde8e4948ef5f092e31","tid":1464730,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:25:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"810c7e2a15f3fcbf81b2cf3b2e7696c1629d4d3c","tid":1464730,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:25:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c1a583197f3101bfc25cb1b6e6fd35a0a9d9044","tid":1464730,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:25:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51bfd70389570173c0ff14c1d3fc3d8d7e9d4fee","tid":1464730,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}